headline: Amazon & OpenAI team up, Microsoft partners with startup Lambda
summary: Yahoo Finance's John Hyland outlines some of the top stories on Wall Street as part of Monday's Market Minute, including Amazon's (AMZN) OpenAI (OPAI.PVT) deal, Microsoft (MSFT) partnering with Lambda (LAMD.PVT), and Ford (F) and Hyundai's (005380.KS) declining electric vehicle (EV) sales. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.

headline: Ford’s EV Sales Plunge. Now We Know What the Tax Credit Meant.
summary: Electric-vehicle sales are going to finish the year terribly, if  Ford Motor’s  October results are any indication.  Monday, Ford released monthly sales for the U.S., saying it sold 175,584 vehicles, up about 2% year over year.  Coming into October, Ford’s U.S. sales were up about 7% year to date.
